{"tid":1682331,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"X邊個都好。唔好搞HKDI副院長。","createTime":"2019-10-30T03:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T13:20:47.000Z","uid":336831,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22d607c48a5948633d8610bea8e24ade274ac5b0","tid":1682331,"uid":336831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:46:22.000Z","msg":"黃副院長雖然無權，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係起碼感受到係同我哋<strong>學生同行</strong><br />\n<br />\n佢同學一齊8個鐘，留到夜晚。<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔似</span></strong></strong>有啲人<span style=\"color: red;\">唔舒服</span>上白車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢會聯同保安部，叫防暴走，確保我哋安全。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔似</span></strong>另外一個肥副院長，得把口。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">最緊要</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n尋晚有同學提供搵鏡頭嘅資料，佢會拿手機影低。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔似</strong></span>有啲人得把口話會跟進。<br />\n<br />\n當時個下同學俾緊資料，有少數同學圍住，佢突然問「有無鏡頭？」，心諗係想搵記者將我哋嘅對話公開。點知吐真心話，係到X班高層。<br />\n<br />\n副校長，我對其他高層都失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n希望你真係俾到信心我哋學生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30/10 13:30 HKDI 見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>和勇一家 遍地開花</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">追究警暴 還原真相</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求推"},{"pid":"b4740d9cdd064dea3ae291d6958212690dcb35aa","tid":1682331,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:47:08.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdb75bc43550b1f608f9fd4a7784eb86d6a6396","tid":1682331,"uid":264746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"HKDI要人 <br />\n今日 1330 交代呀"},{"pid":"1590cecd23c035508aa87a2c60c5bc94462cfb27","tid":1682331,"uid":208402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:52:49.000Z","msg":"di 今日下午停課"},{"pid":"d9565e9fec49cafac02af796afaaa132cf3d219d","tid":1682331,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"點解冇咗件事"},{"pid":"82a83522ec5ba03ca60d64f4f0317b55096490da","tid":1682331,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9565e9fec49cafac02af796afaaa132cf3d219d","tid":1682331,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"點解冇咗件事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"走數囉"},{"pid":"3057764af0fb29446c8623f3f43c08331982e3f9","tid":1682331,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:20:47.000Z","msg":"你講佢屌高層出黎<br />\n係咪想害佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}